Ecological notes : very common in broad-leaved, mixed and carr woodland; arboretum of conifers; grazed wet heathland; wetlands especially fen and bog; also reed and sedge beds, valley and basin mire, pond and lakeside marshes; former gravel workings; calcareous grassland; parkland. iii–xii.
